  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>『モンスター図鑑』について
説明を聞きますか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Do you want to hear about
the 'Monster Book'?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>0</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>聞く</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hear explanation</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Choice 1</Notes>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>聞かない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Skip explanation</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Choice 2</Notes>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>『モンスター図鑑』には、
戦ったモンスターの情報が記録されます</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In the 'Monster Book' you can find
information about the monsters
you've fought.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ただし、外見以外の詳しい情報を集めるには
『スペクタクルズ』などのアイテムで
調べる必要があります</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>However, to gather more detailed
information beyond just their
appearance, you'll need to examine
them using items like 'Magic Lens'.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Unreferenced</Section>
